   "source": "# 子集、排列和组合\n\n这类问题关注“从一组元素中生成所有可能结构”。小规模输入可以直接使用标准库，面试题通常需要掌握回溯写法。\n\n## 排列\n\n给定不含重复元素的整数数组 `nums`，返回所有可能的排列。\n"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": "from itertools import permutations\n\n\ndef permute(nums: list[int]):\n    return list(permutations(nums))\n\n\npermute([1, 2, 3])\n"
  }
 ],
 "metadata": {"kernelspec": {"display_name": "Python 3", "language": "python", "name": "python3"}, "language_info": {"name": "python", "pygments_lexer": "ipython3"}},
